The properties of the Company’s Regulated Businesses consist mainly of approximately:

• 79 surface water treatment plants;

• 530 groundwater treatment plants;

• 150 wastewater treatment plants;

• 53,200 miles of transmission, distribution and collection mains and pipes;

• 1,100 groundwater wells;

• 1,600 water and wastewater pumping stations;

• 1,300 treated water storage facilities; and

• 75 dams.

